This delightful period home blends stylish character with inspirational flair and contemporary style. Offering an exceptional family environment in a most highly regarded pocket of central Sunshine. Other features include ROW access to a tranquil and established garden plus a separate driveway with off street parking.

Description:
Comfort, Style & Convenience
IDEAL INVESTMENT RETURNING $20,340 (approx.) PER ANNUM!
BUILD IN 2017
Welcome to 19 Gardener Drive, this family orientated home is conveniently located in the Saratoga Estate and zoned within the Featherbrook School zone. Offering comfort and convenience located only minutes away from all amenities including a selection of public and private P-9 schools, Featherbrook Shopping Centre and transport links including freeway access.
Appointments include 4 generously sized bedrooms (master bedroom with walk in robe and ensuite, remaining bedrooms with built in robes), contemporary galley style kitchen benefiting from stainless steel appliances, stone stop benches and an abundance of bench/cupboard space overlooking the open living spaces.
A private retreat awaits outdoors enabling you to wine, dine and entertain your guests whilst having the luxury of a backyard with plenty of room the kids and pets to play.
EXTRAS INCLUDE:
Ducted heating and split system cooling for ideal climate control all-year-round, generously sized laundry with external access, remote controlled double garage with internal and rear access, landscaped front and rear gardens, gas hot water system along with a neutral colour scheme and décor throughout.
An inspection is essential to fully appreciate the opportunity on offer.

Description:
Lot 2753 Eskdale Street PREMIUM - THE PROMENADE Collection 3
Create an enviable lifestyle at The Promenade, the gateway to the exceptional Riverwalk Premium within the established Riverwalk community in dynamic Werribee. Surround yourself with natural beauty in this exclusive parkside setting where more than 100,000 sqm of lush Riverfront parkland is just five minutes walk away.
The Promenades impressive entry features a wide tree-lined boulevard delivering a unique opportunity to nestle your dream home amongst mature trees and street landscaping. Enjoy an active lifestyle with the utmost convenience with Lollipop Creek and the Village Park within easy walking distance. A shared path will connect you to the Federation Trail that meanders beside the Werribee River for a scenic journey into the heart of Werribee. Take advantage of regular bus services to the suburbs flourishing amenity from a bus stop right on your doorstep. A premium parkside lifestyle by the river awaits at The Promenade.
A project by Development Victoria. Visit myriverwalk.com.au

Description:
This one's certain to tick all the boxes!
Positioned in a quiet court location is this absolutely stunning family home. Presenting three generous sized fitted bedrooms including oversized master with large walk in robe and ensuite. Upon entry the home showcases a generous sized living space which is flooded with plenty of natural light and offers direct access to the hostess kitchen. Quality slate tiling flows through from the entrance doorway to the open plan family/meals area which boasts a quality timber kitchen with stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances and ample cupboard and clear bench space throughout. Additional appointments include gas ducted heating, air conditioning, freshly painted throughout, brand new carpet and ample storage throughout. Outdoors the home continues to impress comprising of a huge wrap around pergola making the ideal space to entertain friends and family, an expansive double lockup carport and a large established backyard with plenty of open grassed area for the whole family. Located within close proximity to Glen Orden Sports Club, Wyndham Park Community Centre, bus stops, schools, Pacific Werribee shopping complex and Werribee train station. Sitting proudly upon a 565 sqm (Approx.) allotment it's certain this property wont last long. Call to arrange your inspection today!

Description:
Relaxed Living, Convenient Lifestyle
LJ Hooker Point Cook presents 23 Alsace Avenue, Hoppers Crossing. Beautifully modernized and meticulously kept, this splendid single-storey home offers relaxed living and a convenient lifestyle. Unassuming, yet surpassing all expectations, this property comprises two open plan living zones, three bedrooms, two bathrooms and an abundance of outdoor space. Nestled in the quiet Deloraine Estate, this home is surrounded by amenities, with quality schools and childcare centers, major shopping destinations and leisure facilities within easy reach.
- With calming, earth-toned interiors and exceptional natural light, this home offers 22 squares of internal living, beginning with a formal lounge and dining space, perfect for welcoming family and friends. An open plan family and meals zone ensures there's room for the whole family, effortlessly integrating with the huge covered patio, ideal for alfresco dining and sure to please those who love to entertain.
- Remarkably spacious, the open plan kitchen will impress the home chef, with its sunny disposition, wrap around countertops and breakfast bar. A large corner pantry provides excellent storage, while stainless-steel appliances include a gas cooktop, wall mounted oven and dishwasher.
- Three comfortable bedrooms are offered, each generous in size and with built-in robes, roller blinds and soft carpets underfoot. The restful master suite boasts a walk-in-robe and private en suite, the remaining bedrooms sharing access to a central bathroom with a tub and separate toilet.
- Built with integrity by Simmonds Builders, this immaculate 20-year-old property enjoys an expansive 579m2 (approx.) block with lush green gardens, established trees, a fully fenced backyard and an outdoor shed.
- Further highlights include a double garage, an internal laundry, ducted heating, split system air conditioning as well as evaporative cooling throughout.
Enjoying a superb location, this property is within walking distance of the Good News Lutheran P-12 College, The Grange P-12, The Grange Community Centre and Grange Reserve, IGA Hoppers Crossing and Coles Tarneit West. Pacific Werribee, Tarneit Gardens Shopping Centre, Wilmington Kindergarten, Cambridge Primary School and Hoppers Crossing Secondary College are also nearby. Neighbourhood leisure precincts include Hogans Road Reserve, Riverbend Historical Park and Cambridge Reserve, while public transportation options include Hoppers Crossing station and well serviced bus routes.
Note. All stated dimensions are approximate only. Particulars given are for general information only and do not constitute any representation on the part of the vendor or agent.

Description:
Titled And Ready To Build, Grand Central Estate, Tarneit
Bal & Ray White Truganina exclusively presents you this perfect opportunity to purchase this easement free title block of land to build your dream home in the ever growing and demanding Grand Central Estate in Tarneit. Grand central estate will be home to plenty of fantastic amenities, including schools, shopping, childcare, community center and beautiful parks with amazing playground.
Grand Central, a perfect blend of urban greenery and sculpture in an active community. With established landscaping and public art to beautify the lush open spaces, this development is designed to evoke a sense of home at first glance. A community designed for easy living where residents can move around their community, accessing public transport, green pedestrian linkages with the aim of connecting residents to all the amenities within and around Grand Central.
Transport connection With a future train station coming to Tarneit as part of the State Government's Network Development Plan to support future population growth, this community is well positioned to provide connectivity and contribute to a positive eco foot print with a proposed commute into the CBD of just 32 minutes.
The township of Tarneit is also well-serviced by multiple bus routes. If you prefer to drive, access to the CBD from the nearby Princes Freeway (M1) is moments away. Tarneit Town Centre is a thriving local retail precinct offering a range of supermarkets, speciality stores and ambient cafes and eateries.
Just 3.2km away is the recently revitalized Pacific Werribee, featuring Target, Big W, Coles, Kmart, Woolworths, Best & Less, JB Hi-Fi and over 300 speciality stores.
The nearby future town centre offers Grand Central residents a major centre within walking distance of home. With leading brands, bars and restaurants, supermarkets and a town square, every convenience will be within reach.
Dont miss this Opportunity!!! Build your Dream house!!!
Please Contact Bal on 0413 870 550 or Harpreet on 0416 412 414 now for more details as this one won't last long.

Description:
Love the Home and the Location
Contemporary class sets off this beautiful, family friendly home. Spacious interiors and a flowing floor plan combine to create a highly desirable living environment. An established garden setting plus a quiet location close to all facilities further enhance the desirability of this outstanding family home.
Four bedrooms plus study and two bathrooms. Spacious main bedroom with large walk in robe and en suite bathroom with stone benchtops
A choice of living areas includes formal lounge and dining area flowing through to the informal living area comprising of modern kitchen, large island bench with ample storage and breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, stone benchtops throughout plus pantry, adjoining meals and living room
Living areas open to the paved alfresco and extensive decked area surrounded by the landscaped low maintenance garden surrounds complete with mature trees and plantings plus artificial turfed area, a great area for relaxing or entertaining
Features include heating and cooling, double car garage with internal and rear access, security alarm, neutral décor and colour scheme, quality fixtures and fittings including quality flooring, window furnishings, high ceilings, feature lighting and downlights, landscaped low maintenance garden surrounds front and rear and so much more
Outstanding location with schools, public transport, shopping and parkland close by, this home ticks all the boxes and is sure to impress inspection will not disappoint.
